## ğŸ¯ Offsets

Push items to the right with `offset`.

```tsx
<Grid container spacing={3}>
  <Grid size={{ xs: 6, md: 2 }} offset={{ xs: 3, md: 0 }}>
    <Item>Offset Grid</Item>
  </Grid>
</Grid>
```

- `offset={2}` shifts the item right by 2 columns.
- `offset="auto"` aligns the item to the right.

